Package armidale.api.gui

Interface Summary
Action All gui widgets that interact with the user are derived ultimately from the ActionWidget interface.
ActionCallback a callback which signals an action event associated with the object
BorderPanel A BorderPanel is a panel on which widgets are layed out using a border layout manager.
